<title>HONG KONG: Rhine interim net loss HK$69.76 mln.</title>
<headline>Rhine interim net loss HK$69.76 mln.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1996-09-26</dateline>
<text>
<p>Six months ended June 30</p>
<p>(in million HK$ unless stated)</p>
<p>    Shr (H.K. cents)	   45.5 loss  vs 6.87 gain (adjusted)</p>
<p>    Dividend (H.K. cents)    nil	  vs nil</p>
<p>    Extraordinary items	58.37 loss vs nil</p>
<p>    Net			    69.76 loss vs 8.89 profit</p>
<p>    Turnover		     219.77     vs 253.11</p>
<p>    Company name		 Rhine Holdings Ltd</p>
<p>    Books close		  N/A</p>
<p>    Dividend payable	   N/A</p>
<p>NOTE - Rhine Holdings is a jewellery manufacturer.</p>
<p>Net is after an exceptional loss on provision against inventories, provision against debtors, provision for closure of retail shops and business restructuring costs.</p>
<p>Comparative share earnings have been adjusted for a 3-for-5 bonus share issue and 4-into-1 share consolidation.</p>
<p>-- Hong Kong Newsroom (852) 2843 6368</p>
